OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775131865
OL,3,CPrincess Royal's son to marry NHS
OL,4,Cnurse in summer wedding
OL,6,FThe Princess Royal's son Peter
OL,7,FPhillips is set to marry fiancee
OL,8,FHarriet Sperling at a summer wedding
OL,9,Fin the Cotswolds, it has been
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FThe late Queen Elizabeth II's eldest
OL,13,Fgrandson will tie the knot with NHS
OL,14,Fnurse Ms Sperling in a private
OL,15,Fceremony at All Saints Church in the
OL,16,Fvillage of Kemble, near Cirencester on
OL,17,FSaturday 6 June.
OL,26,@oD@_rr
