PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775131865
OL,3,CPrincess Royal's son to marry NHS
OL,4,Cnurse in summer wedding
OL,6,FThe King and Queen and the Prince and
OL,7,FPrincess of Wales have been informed
OL,8,Fof the announcement, a spokesman for
OL,9,FMr Phillips confirmed.
OL,11,FThe low-key wedding is likely to see
OL,12,Fthe royal family descend on the
OL,13,FGloucestershire village for the
OL,14,Fcelebration.
OL,16,FBoth of the couple's families have
OL,17,Fbeen informed of the wedding date by
OL,18,Finvitation, the spokesman added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
