PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775131865
OL,3,CPrincess Royal's son to marry NHS
OL,4,Cnurse in summer wedding
OL,6,FMr Phillips, 48, is the King's nephew,
OL,7,FWilliam and the Duke of Sussex's
OL,8,Fcousin, the brother of Zara Tindall,
OL,9,Fand the son of Anne and her first
OL,10,Fhusband Captain Mark Phillips.
OL,12,FAll Saints Church, with its tall
OL,13,Fspire, sits in the heart of Kemble,
OL,14,Fwith its congregation described as
OL,15,F"very much involved in village life".
OL,17,FMr Phillips lives nearby on his
OL,18,Fmother's Gatcombe Park estate in
OL,19,FMinchinhampton.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@dO]
