PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775131865
OL,3,CPrincess Royal's son to marry NHS
OL,4,Cnurse in summer wedding
OL,6,FHe split from his first wife Autumn in
OL,7,F2020 after 12 years of marriage and
OL,8,Fshares custody of their two children,
OL,9,FSavannah, 15, and 14-year-old Isla.
OL,11,FThe pair married in a grand royal
OL,12,Fwedding in St George's Chapel, Windsor
OL,13,FCastle, in 2008.
OL,15,FMr Phillips' engagement to Ms
OL,16,FSperling, who he began dating in 2024,
OL,17,Fwas announced in August last year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
